# Research: the Honest Spoken Record for Judging

## Question

session.history loses interrupted/list turns (receipt: "The six that need
you:" saved with no list; caller audibly heard it). The judge must score what
was actually SAID. Investigate livekit-agents 1.4.x: transcription/spoken-sync
events, per-segment callbacks, whether interrupted content is truncated or
dropped, and whether our Convex turn rows / transcriptLine field can carry the
true record. Deliverable: an asset stating the recommended capture mechanism
